items.title: NYLI Epoch Global Equity Yield ADR SMA Q1 2025 Commentary
items.description: For the quarter, NYLI Epoch Global Equity Yield ADR SMA posted a return of 5.1% (Gross) and 4.3% (Net) while the broad market returned negative 1.8% as measured by the MSCI World Index.

items.title: This CEO went from folding clothes at Nordstrom to being Jeff Bezos’ right hand man—the billionaire told him to delegate to his employees more
items.description: Amazon’s Jeff Bezos taught Coursera’s new chief executive Greg Hart the fewer decisions that have to go to the CEO, the better.
